	Add a way to specify the tag used in syncGet.
	* include/urbi/usyncclient.hh,
	* src/liburbi/usyncclient.cc: Here.
	(syncGet_): New. Gets tag to use and optional modifiers (+end...).
	(syncGet): Changed to wrapper on syncGet_.
	(syncGetTag): New. Wrapper on syncGet_. Takes user specified tag and
	tag options.

