	* src/liburbi/uobject.cc: Here.

2007-11-20  Matthieu Nottale  <nottale@gostai.com>

	Fix race condition.
	* src/examples/urbiping.cc: Change behavior when a 0-interval is
	  passed to send pings without any sleep() call.
	* src/liburbi/ucallbacks.cc: Do not insert ourselve in hash from 
	  base class to avoid a race condition. Do it in registerCallback().
	* src/liburbi/uobject/urbi/ucallbacks.hh.template: Call
	  registerCallback.

