	notifychange/access, introduce back_cast to cast any->uvalue
	* src/liburbi/uobject/urbi/uobject.hh.template: 
	    - Add a bool to GenericCallbac ctor and all createcallbacks.
	    - Casting from any type to UValue is not done by UValue
	cast operators but by calling the back_cast method. 
