2006-12-19  Jean-Christophe Baillie  <baillie@gostai.com>

	Add support for kernel system message through the USystem API.
	UObjects that inherit from USystem will have access to the
	register_channel and receive_message methods to handle system
	messages, only in pluggin mode.

	Add support for kernel system messages in UObject with USystem
	* src/liburbi/Makefile.am: add usystem in the compile process.
	* src/liburbi/uobject/uobject.mk: add usystem to install process.
	* src/liburbi/uobject/urbi/usystem.hh: New.
	* src/liburbi/usystem.cc: New.

