2006-09-29  matthieu nottale  <nottale@gostai.com>

	umake fixes

	* sdk/umake-engine: New.
	* sdk/umake-lib: New.
	* sdk/install: New. Install script, required if sdk must be relocated
	* sdk/umake.in: Default core is now HARDCODED to 'remote'. Pass
	prefix to param.mk, so it can be location-independant.
	* sdk/Makefile.am: Install install.
	* sdk/param.mk.in: Remove ref to prefix.
	* src/liburbi/Makefile.am: Add correct libjpegx to libkernel so
	that libjpeg is linked in the lib.
	* lib/jpeg-6b/Makefile.am: libjpegx.la is built, as a
	noninstallable conveninance lib.

2006-09-28  matthieu nottale  <nottale@gostai.com>

	Umake improvments

	* sdk/umake.in: Defaults link with default core (according to jcb
	spec). Option -l produces only a library. Default target name
	depends on host and core.
	* sdk/param.mk.in: Fix to better handle dependency: two generic
	targets (%.a and .cc:.lo) where resulting in the .lo files being
	deleted by make.

